		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I do have here a very funny method to clean those game connectors: take a little bit of vinegar and put salt in it until it begins to saturate. Then use a Q-Tip and you'll notice that it will clean out quite fast these connectors. BTW you can use that solution for pennies as well

		

